{"tid":1494786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推比記者問江永祥：而家唔係「相嗌唔好口喎」，係你隊成個警隊內部都咁樣標籤示威者，你仲洗唔洗fact check?","createTime":"2019-08-21T19:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T08:59:42.000Z","uid":279616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91944ab6069f314214654b77747ec90d313629a2","tid":1494786,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"推比記者問江永祥：而家唔係「相嗌唔好口喎」，係成個警隊內部都咁樣標籤示威者，全部當值警員都聽到，你仲洗唔洗fact check?對警隊咁既作為有咩評論？知唔知歷史上幾時出現過「去人化」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撇除政府問題，淨係計警隊，再淨係計721 85 811 新屋嶺 CCTV直送，已經夠哂理由比示威者做任何野，包括以武制暴 以眼還眼 百倍奉還<br />\n<br />\n重申七一宣言，設立死線，立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n「勇武派」、「和理非」係角色，唔係派系，理念一致，只係手法不同<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#唔撤就罷<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 刑事追究 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"d6e5ab177191c908a50ddacb864078dca525fd8c","tid":1494786,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:09:17.000Z","msg":"幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛國既中國人做咩要o係海外留學<br />\n中國既學校唔好咩？<br />\n推到愛國中國人返中國讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08wCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=79ae3dcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests</a>"},{"pid":"74b19524ecb29ca02e24bcfb805dfb9cda2da960","tid":1494786,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:09:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曱甴論同中國用納粹手勢敬禮 推動種族仇恨</span></span>"},{"pid":"bcdadb7f60b9edde48c72d372c9c6dae6ac989db","tid":1494786,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}